arChildNodes.szComment: Abasi speaks to the worth of a "warrior's heart," as seen by his people.
Abasi speaks to the location of Nyamoyo's ancient shrine.
Abasi speaks to Nyamoyo taking a warrior's heart so that they may "live" beyond death--remembered and heard across Teganze.
Abasi speaks to Nyamoyo's gift allowing a warrior to "live" with their loved ones,  even when they are gone in body--sombre in recognising his own mortality, limited time with his daughter.
Abasi confidently calls to move to the ritual site--sensing Nyamoyo's eagerness.
